<paragraph blockId="0.[1260,2140,1210,1479]" pageId="0" pageNumber="536">• (Coastal areas in central Chile, pre-Andean and Andean regions, desert and semi-desert scrublands, rainforests, and Mediterranean habitats.</paragraph>
